AF_UNSPEC - ADDRESS FAMILY IS UNSPECIFIED
AI_PASSIVE - BY WHICH WE GET OUR OWN IP ADDRESS
AI = Address Info

0 means it is never going to timeout. We keep a timeout sometimes for security reasons, when we don't want it running throughout

FD_ISSET is the method that looks through the list and checks which filedescriptors have events

inet_ntop - converts ip address to printable form

Use select instead of accept for continuous connection